column4:
I fucking love that you are majority owner of Twitter . My friends David and Daniel have a
program that verifies identity that would be nice to connect to Twitter . As in , if people chose
to use it , it could verify that they are a real person and not a troll farm . I should introduce you
to them .
I just own 9 % of Twitter , so don't control the company .
Will raise the identity issue with Parag ( CEO ) .
